items.storedetaileddescription: Walker Tape®’s Sponge Brushes make it easy to offer safe and sanitary services to multiple clients. They make it easy to spread adhesives, solvents, or preparation product evenly without the worry of losing brush hairs in adhesive. A great single-use option for stylists to prevent cross-contamination.
items.outofstockbehavior: Allow back orders with no out-of-stock message
